Project: Airport Management System (Milestone 2)

Language Used: Python 3
Database: SQLite

How to Run:

1. Open terminal in project folder
2. Run: python main.py

Files Included:

* main.py
* airport.db
* schema.sql
* sample_data.sql

Features:

* Search flight by flight number
* Search trip (direct and connecting flights)
* Seat availability check
* Passenger itinerary retrieval

Notes:

* No GUI (Milestone 2 requirement)
* All features run through command line
 